	<h2> Introduction: </h2>
	<p> The first-ever anime screening event at the Indian Institute of Technology Kharagpur (IIT Kharagpur) took place with electrifying enthusiasm and excitement on Sunday, 9:00 pm 13th August, 2023. The event was centred around the highly anticipated showcase of the single greatest powerup in anime history,<i> Gear 5</i> of <i>One Piece</i>. It drew in a huge crowd of avid anime enthusiasts among the IIT KGP junta who were eager to experience the thrill of watching their favourite show on the big (larger-than-life) screen with their friends. </p>
	
	<h2> Motivation for the event: </h2>
	<p> The revelation of Luffy's Gear Fifth transformation in the beloved anime and manga series "One Piece" sent shockwaves through the internet, causing an unprecedented surge in online activity. Fans worldwide were left awestruck as they witnessed Luffy's astounding power evolution, with his body adorned in enigmatic and awe-inspiring new abilities. This sparked an electrifying wave of fervour and exhilaration among the vibrant anime and manga loving community of IIT Kharagpur students. The hostels buzzed with energy as students from diverse disciplines united in their shared enthusiasm, organising impromptu gatherings and viewing parties in their rooms/labs to collectively join in the revelation and forge lasting bonds over their mutual adoration for this groundbreaking moment of <i>One Piece</i>. <b>MASK</b> took this opportunity to amplify the excitement to a fever pitch by organising a screening of the three latest episodes: E1070, E1071 & E1072, in Netaji Auditorium, the theatre hall of IIT KGP. </p>
