	<h2> Event Highlights: </h2>
	<p> The atmosphere buzzed with anticipation as excited students formed a spirited crowd outside “Netaji Auditorium”, eagerly waiting to join in on the excitement for the historic anime screening event, the first of many more to come. Almost an hour before the event's commencement, a dedicated crowd showed up early, determined to claim the best seats in the house. Their enthusiasm was palpable, reflecting the fervour and passion that <i>One Piece</i> fans held for this exclusive experience. As the doors finally swung open, the early birds revelled in their victory, occupying the centre rows with triumphant smiles, ready to immerse themselves in the world of <i>One Piece</i>. The organisers, <b>MASK</b>, had spared no effort in creating an immersive experience, by booking the revered theatre which is complete with comfortable seating arrangements, high-quality projection equipment, and surround sound. Attendees were treated to a visually stunning journey into the world of <i>One Piece</i> as they awaited the unveiling of the much-talked-about <i>Gear 5</i>. </p>
