	<h2> Pre-Screening Activities: </h2>
	<p> In the spirited pre-screening activity organised by <b>MASK</b>, they displayed their creative prowess through captivating Anime Music Video (AMV) showcases. With an artful blend of iconic anime scenes, meticulously timed to a harmonious medley of music, the AMV captivated the audience and set the stage for an immersive anime experience. The skillful editing, emotional resonance, and sheer dedication showcased in the AMV highlighted the depth of talent within the AMV team of <b>MASK</b>, leaving the audience eagerly anticipating the main event of the <i>One Piece</i>,<i> Gear 5</i> screening. There were three AMVs showcased from Garden of Words, School Babysitters and Assasination Classroom, prior to which the theatre echoed with music from Radwimps from the beloved anime movie, Your Name, while masterfully showcasing the <b>MASK</b> logo on screen. </p>
